                <div><strong>Livros de Cálculo I e II</strong><br><small class="text-muted">R$ 180</small></div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586023492125-27b2c045efd7?q=80" class="product-thumb me-3" alt="Cadeira">
